description: Watch out for Acacia Cafe on the roads of Rhode Island if you’re in the mood to munch on delicious sandwiches and soups; all internationally inspired, all made with locally sourced produce, all delicious. Taste their perfect Thai Banh Mi or treat yourself to the Meatloaf Sandwich of your dreams, and there's so much more. Their weekly specials include Vegan, Vegetarian, and Gluten Free options, so for a scrumptious and healthy lunch on the run, you gotta check out this truck that’s Straight Outta Little Compton.
name: Acacia Cafe Food Truck
